../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:5:This chain is honest about the Tao filter and legitimately targets something the averaged model may destroy. That is the good part.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:28:- The step assumes there is a clean "averaged-model counterpart at the same level of description." That is not automatic. Tao's averaged equation is not just "NS with slightly modified triad coefficients." The comparison can become representation-dependent and technically slippery.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:30:- "Isolate what averaging preserves and what it destroys" is necessary but insufficient. Averaging can destroy exact geometry while preserving enough effective interaction strength that no regularity leverage remains. The chain risks mistaking "not identical" for "operationally distinguishable."
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:31:- The kill condition uses "same effective strength," but effective strength is undefined. Is that pointwise in the symbol? averaged over orientations? after frequency summation? after localization? after time averaging? Without that definition, the gate can be passed or failed by rhetoric.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:70:The chain treats "exact NS triad geometry differs from Tao-averaged geometry" as though this is already close to a breakthrough criterion. It is not. The missing ingredient is a mechanism that survives summation, localization, and dynamics. The chain acknowledges this only late.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:72:### 2. It is too close to harmonic-analysis territory to feel safely beyond Tao
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:74:Helical decomposition and triad bookkeeping are more refined than generic Littlewood-Paley estimates, but they are still heavily spectral and harmonic-analysis adjacent. Unless the chain isolates a genuinely algebraic NS-only sign or forbidden transfer that the averaged model destroys, it risks staying inside the spirit of Tao's obstruction while believing it has escaped.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:101:- Step 2 at least tries to compare exact NS against Tao's obstruction at the right conceptual interface.
