  geometry route died. Result: the geometry branch was already killed on its
  fixed Eulerian package, so this step should not revive it except as negative
  background.
- The active task is now the exact-reformulation cleanup branch selected after
  replanning. This step must freeze one inherited architecture, one named bad
  term, one compatible solution class, one localization protocol, one gain
  currency, and a bounded `2-3` item reformulation family before any Tao screen
  or estimate ledger is allowed.
- Because the step requires new explorations, query the receptionist first for
