    pressure obstruction and the killed geometry branch;
  - localization and compatibility constraints already documented in the local
    library;
  - the most natural exact reformulation family already suggested by the chain
    record and planning materials.
- Planned exploration structure, subject to receptionist guidance:
  - Exploration 001: architecture and bottleneck choice
