+
+## Output Requirements
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
+
+Use source-based labels such as `[VERIFIED]`, `[INFERRED]`, and `[PROPOSED]`.
+Keep the conclusion narrow and tied to the fixed LEI architecture.
